cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.DC

This paper discusses a new high-level interface to multi-threading in Prolog, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses different types of explicit parallelism, which can be categorized under logic in computer science (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the interface in hProlog, which can be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
